  description: "I fail to realize it's you. I want to keep going, but I just don\u2019t
    have the strength to endure anymore. I want to give us one last chance, but I
    can\u2019t handle feeling worthless anymore. This relationship will only move
    forward if you\u2019re willing to take my hand and lift me up... or let me go."
